        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "*Index of life expectancy, education and income per person Sources: Transparency International; UN Development Programme; Alina Mungiu-Pippidi, LUISS Guido Carli University",
        "bbox": [
          0.37093690848511,
          0.3080357141211962,
